{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"b9c34b5a-b0f5-44d9-9e90-7d404c57e6aa","content":"Good news — on .NET 10 SDK, `dotnet test` **natively speaks MTP**. The `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` property was a .NET 9-era opt-in bridge and is **no longer needed**. You can simply remove it.\n\nYou still need `EnableMSTestRunner` (it tells MSTest to produce the executable test host that MTP requires).\n\nHere's the fix:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"tooluse_thDgLGK2ER712USeZTLUNY","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Removing obsolete MTP property"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"tooluse_BTje1YMDJziRl9KnKDBCSr","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-e61c03430fe9466bac8de8b3c03112d7/TestProject.csproj","old_str":"    <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>\n    <TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>","new_str":"    <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"edit the file at /tmp/sv-e61c03430fe9466bac8de8b3c03112d7/TestProject.csproj."}],"interactionId":"9d4a14c3-09be-4586-b5a7-3206e32b8565","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is on .NET 10 SDK (10.0.100) and wants to know about Microsoft.Testing.Platform (MTP) support. Let me provide accurate information.\n\nIn .NET 10, `dotnet test` natively supports Microsoft.Testing.Platform (MTP) without needing the `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` property. The .NET 10 SDK ships with a new `dotnet test` that uses MTP by default.\n\nKey points:\n1. In .NET 10, `dotnet test` has been rewritten to natively support MTP.\n2. `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` is no longer needed — it was a bridge property for .NET 9 SDK to opt into MTP support.\n\n\n3. `EnableMSTestRunner` is still required to generate an executable test host.\n4. The user should remove `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` from their project file since it's not needed on .NET 10.","outputTokens":565,"requestId":"E82A:11815A:26C21C5:293D644:6A049419"},"id":"82a78174-4742-41a1-9d26-769b598fc63b","timestamp":"2026-05-13T15:09:25.236Z","parentId":"89cf8f27-c70f-4f5c-9c82-5b62eaa18a65"}
